ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606610/extras/51ca6c5c96eb5ba7f1fcb216ec5fef69.avif?t=1747508875\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><strong> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Collectibles available on the map.<br></li><li> Customizable weapons</li></ul></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606610/extras/f672b2f7196a37d10cac544ef5a2406b.avif?t=1747508875\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><i> The Rutianland region is scattered with details, items and easter eggs. Explore, discover, have fun!</i><br><br><strong> Master everything in Rescuer! </strong>",
